Modifications:
-- Modified Injector to remove Android specific code to use Linux process injection
-- Restructured io to use a hybrid of evilsocket and Chanfire interfaces and Kubo hooking
-- Restructed injector to use hybrid of Kubo and Colgan for Ubuntu 18.04 and Arm64
-- Adaptations for arm64, x86, and x86-64 support
-- Removed cflumen directory

